1
00:01:30,220 --> 00:01:32,980
Episode 10

2
00:01:37,200 --> 00:01:38,310
Time to go!

3
00:01:38,350 --> 00:01:38,870
Alright!

4
00:01:39,480 --> 00:01:40,200
Leave it to me!

5
00:01:40,310 --> 00:01:41,680
It's okay. It's not heavy.

6
00:01:41,680 --> 00:01:42,280
I'll handle it.

7
00:01:42,280 --> 00:01:42,840
You put it down.

8
00:01:43,640 --> 00:01:44,400
We're waiting for you!

9
00:01:44,400 --> 00:01:44,950
Hurry, help me!

10
00:01:44,950 --> 00:01:45,870
Give it to me! Come on!

11
00:01:47,070 --> 00:01:47,590
Take it easy.

12
00:01:50,710 --> 00:01:51,870
I'll return on the 18th this month.

13
00:01:53,760 --> 00:01:54,710
I know your train number.

14
00:01:55,000 --> 00:01:56,400
I'll go pick you up at the station.

15
00:01:57,430 --> 00:01:58,590
Don't forget me.

16
00:02:00,870 --> 00:02:01,590
After the separation,

17
00:02:01,590 --> 00:02:02,870
who knows when

18
00:02:04,480 --> 00:02:05,480
the three of us

19
00:02:05,480 --> 00:02:06,920
will meet again.

20
00:02:09,870 --> 00:02:11,750
It's Lunar New Year. Why are you crying?

21
00:02:12,960 --> 00:02:14,280
Long distance separates no friends.

22
00:02:15,400 --> 00:02:16,910
We have telephones now.

23
00:02:16,910 --> 00:02:18,030
I'll call you when I miss you.

24
00:02:18,030 --> 00:02:18,870
Don't you dare not reply.

25
00:02:19,520 --> 00:02:20,960
As if I would!

26
00:02:24,240 --> 00:02:25,190
Alright, alright.

27
00:02:26,910 --> 00:02:28,080
Remember to miss me.

28
00:02:28,280 --> 00:02:29,560
Take care of yourselves.

29
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:53,680
I'm so glad I still have you.

30
00:03:08,910 --> 00:03:09,560
Who are you?

31
00:03:10,280 --> 00:03:10,710
Sir,

32
00:03:11,400 --> 00:03:12,630
I'm here for my daughter.

33
00:03:12,910 --> 00:03:14,120
I'm taking her home for the festival.

34
00:03:14,630 --> 00:03:15,800
She works here at the cafeteria

35
00:03:15,800 --> 00:03:16,520
as a helper.

36
00:03:16,710 --> 00:03:17,630
There's no one on this

37
00:03:17,630 --> 00:03:18,430
construction site.

38
00:03:19,030 --> 00:03:20,240
Where did everyone go?

39
00:03:20,710 --> 00:03:21,470
Holiday break.

40
00:03:21,800 --> 00:03:22,470
They all left.

41
00:03:23,080 --> 00:03:23,680
That can't be.

42
00:03:23,870 --> 00:03:24,630
She's got nowhere else.

43
00:03:25,030 --> 00:03:25,560
Sir,

44
00:03:26,560 --> 00:03:27,190
can I leave my ID

45
00:03:27,190 --> 00:03:27,960
here as a guarantee?

46
00:03:28,190 --> 00:03:28,630
Look,

47
00:03:29,590 --> 00:03:30,190
this is me.

48
00:03:30,840 --> 00:03:31,400
You can have it.

49
00:03:31,430 --> 00:03:32,280
You don't believe me?

50
00:03:32,280 --> 00:03:34,000
I told you there's no one inside.

51
00:03:34,030 --> 00:03:35,000
I just want to take a look.

52
00:03:35,360 --> 00:03:35,800
Sir,

53
00:03:35,870 --> 00:03:36,750
I won't cause any trouble.

54
00:03:37,120 --> 00:03:38,150
Just one look, and I'll leave.

55
00:03:42,030 --> 00:03:42,910
Hello?

56
00:03:46,030 --> 00:03:46,870
Wanzhi!

57
00:03:49,150 --> 00:03:50,280
Fang Wanzhi!

58
00:03:53,590 --> 00:03:54,310
Wanzhi!

59
00:03:56,280 --> 00:03:56,870
Wanzhi!

60
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:44,600
Cloud.

61
00:04:44,950 --> 00:04:45,430
Yes.

62
00:05:10,720 --> 00:05:11,560
(Buji Town,)

63
00:05:12,070 --> 00:05:14,070
(a place on the outskirts of Shenzhen,)

64
00:05:14,510 --> 00:05:16,600
(will be my new starting point.)

65
00:05:17,160 --> 00:05:18,390
(The road to success)

66
00:05:18,720 --> 00:05:20,560
(is never a simple sum,)

67
00:05:20,870 --> 00:05:23,430
(but the cruel arithmetic
of choice and cost.)

68
00:05:24,270 --> 00:05:26,240
(I'll trade my current struggles)

69
00:05:26,510 --> 00:05:28,390
(for a bright future.)

70
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:29,720
(In my books,)

71
00:05:30,190 --> 00:05:31,160
(that's a worthy trade.)

72
00:05:34,160 --> 00:05:35,430
Which one of you is Pei?

73
00:05:37,480 --> 00:05:38,360
You must be the girl

74
00:05:38,360 --> 00:05:39,680
who's here to rent the room, right?

75
00:05:39,750 --> 00:05:40,750
One moment, please.

76
00:05:40,950 --> 00:05:41,870
Hurry up!

77
00:05:42,310 --> 00:05:42,950
Hey, wait!

78
00:05:44,480 --> 00:05:45,360
I won!

79
00:05:46,750 --> 00:05:47,950
Pay up, pay up!

80
00:05:48,000 --> 00:05:49,240
You've got to be kidding me!

81
00:05:49,240 --> 00:05:51,920
(Spring Festival is when
Shenzhen is least crowded,)

82
00:05:52,310 --> 00:05:54,070
(but also when people
find the most chances.)

83
00:05:54,800 --> 00:05:55,390
(I believe)

84
00:05:55,680 --> 00:05:58,360
(this may be the opportunity
for me to truly stand firm)

85
00:05:58,560 --> 00:05:59,950
(in this city.)

86
00:06:00,390 --> 00:06:01,480
(I told myself...)

87
00:06:01,920 --> 00:06:02,560
(Shenzhen,)

88
00:06:02,950 --> 00:06:05,070
(I'd spend the festival with you.)

89
00:06:05,480 --> 00:06:06,390
This is the room.

90
00:06:06,560 --> 00:06:07,000
Look,

91
00:06:07,310 --> 00:06:07,830
isn't it nice?

92
00:06:08,070 --> 00:06:08,920
This is

93
00:06:08,950 --> 00:06:10,240
the nicest room I have.

94
00:06:10,310 --> 00:06:11,070
Look over here.

95
00:06:12,190 --> 00:06:13,480
See these two windows?

96
00:06:13,630 --> 00:06:14,870
They provide great lighting.

97
00:06:15,190 --> 00:06:16,270
Look at all the sunlight.

98
00:06:16,430 --> 00:06:18,240
It's warm in winter and cool in summer.

99
00:06:21,120 --> 00:06:21,600
Ah, yes.

100
00:06:21,630 --> 00:06:22,480
That side faces south,

101
00:06:22,560 --> 00:06:23,270
and this one north.

102
00:06:23,390 --> 00:06:24,390
The room's cross-ventilated

103
00:06:24,510 --> 00:06:26,120
with excellent Fengshui.

104
00:06:29,000 --> 00:06:30,070
The place is okay,

105
00:06:30,430 --> 00:06:32,480
but the bathroom is too far.

106
00:06:32,510 --> 00:06:33,720
And there's no kitchen either.

107
00:06:34,240 --> 00:06:35,270
That can be a problem.

108
00:06:35,430 --> 00:06:36,190
For the bathroom,

109
00:06:36,240 --> 00:06:37,390
I can't help you with that.

110
00:06:37,560 --> 00:06:39,270
But you can set up a
kitchen here yourself.

111
00:06:39,270 --> 00:06:40,750
It won't cost much.

112
00:06:40,870 --> 00:06:43,560
Most importantly, the rent is low.

113
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:45,720
I've long heard people from Buji

114
00:06:45,720 --> 00:06:46,800
are great at business.

115
00:06:47,040 --> 00:06:47,950
I really need to negotiate

116
00:06:47,950 --> 00:06:48,870
the price with you.

117
00:06:49,120 --> 00:06:50,720
This isn't just for me, after all.

118
00:06:51,000 --> 00:06:52,070
I have to take responsibility

119
00:06:52,070 --> 00:06:53,190
for my roommates.

120
00:06:54,120 --> 00:06:55,240
I'm not from Buji.

121
00:06:55,390 --> 00:06:57,270
I'm married to someone from Buji.

122
00:06:57,560 --> 00:06:58,720
Twenty years ago,

123
00:06:58,750 --> 00:07:00,390
I married into his family.

124
00:07:00,560 --> 00:07:01,630
The rent

125
00:07:01,630 --> 00:07:02,750
is non-negotiable.

126
00:07:02,950 --> 00:07:03,920
The most important thing is

127
00:07:03,950 --> 00:07:05,560
that you won't find a cheaper place

128
00:07:05,680 --> 00:07:06,680
anywhere in Shenzhen

129
00:07:06,720 --> 00:07:08,240
even if you try.

130
00:07:12,430 --> 00:07:13,000
Fine.

131
00:07:13,240 --> 00:07:14,190
Let's do monthly payments.

132
00:07:14,270 --> 00:07:14,800
No.

133
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:15,680
Minimum six months.

134
00:07:16,040 --> 00:07:16,680
Three months.

135
00:07:16,870 --> 00:07:17,950
Are you serious?

136
00:07:17,950 --> 00:07:18,950
If you don't want to rent it,

137
00:07:18,950 --> 00:07:20,430
don't disturb my mahjong game.

138
00:07:20,870 --> 00:07:21,430
Ma'am!

139
00:07:22,190 --> 00:07:22,830
Ma'am,

140
00:07:24,560 --> 00:07:26,190
I just came to Shenzhen to work,

141
00:07:26,510 --> 00:07:27,480
and I haven't saved up,

142
00:07:28,120 --> 00:07:29,600
neither have I landed a new job.

143
00:07:30,160 --> 00:07:31,430
Please cut me some slack.

144
00:07:32,430 --> 00:07:34,190
It's easy to find a job here,

145
00:07:34,510 --> 00:07:36,160
especially for pretty girls.

146
00:07:36,480 --> 00:07:37,630
No matter where you are,

147
00:07:37,800 --> 00:07:39,630
good people are bound to get rich.

148
00:07:41,120 --> 00:07:41,920
When I was little,

149
00:07:41,950 --> 00:07:43,680
everyone called me Lucky Star.

150
00:07:44,120 --> 00:07:45,600
If I can move in,

151
00:07:45,750 --> 00:07:46,310
maybe

152
00:07:46,360 --> 00:07:47,600
you'll win every time at mahjong.

153
00:07:49,630 --> 00:07:50,750
Well said!

154
00:07:51,510 --> 00:07:53,920
That's the best thing you've said!

155
00:07:54,480 --> 00:07:55,920
Three months it is.

156
00:07:56,040 --> 00:07:56,950
When you become a big boss,

157
00:07:57,270 --> 00:07:58,270
don't forget about me.

158
00:07:58,920 --> 00:07:59,630
Thank you, ma'am.

159
00:08:00,360 --> 00:08:01,040
My surname is Pei.

160
00:08:01,160 --> 00:08:02,360
Just call me Pei.

161
00:08:03,310 --> 00:08:04,870
Just because of this unlucky surname,

162
00:08:04,920 --> 00:08:06,720
I lose money every day.

163
00:08:08,120 --> 00:08:09,270
What the hell?

164
00:08:10,070 --> 00:08:11,160
I'm finally

165
00:08:11,160 --> 00:08:12,190
getting lucky today!

166
00:08:12,190 --> 00:08:13,190
You want to win? Heh!

167
00:08:15,160 --> 00:08:17,120
Give the change!

168
00:08:17,120 --> 00:08:18,720
Come on! Why do I have
to give the change?

169
00:08:23,310 --> 00:08:23,830
Hello?

170
00:08:24,510 --> 00:08:25,310
Grandma Yu!

171
00:08:25,600 --> 00:08:26,630
This is Wanzhi.

172
00:08:27,560 --> 00:08:28,680
Is everything okay?

173
00:08:28,870 --> 00:08:29,720
Wanzhi!

174
00:08:30,070 --> 00:08:31,720
Yes, everything's fine.

175
00:08:33,080 --> 00:08:34,080
Is he home?

176
00:08:34,630 --> 00:08:35,600
You mean your dad?

177
00:08:36,200 --> 00:08:37,670
He went to Shenzhen to pick you up.

178
00:08:37,910 --> 00:08:38,390
(What?)

179
00:08:38,720 --> 00:08:39,600
(You didn't see him?)

180
00:08:40,270 --> 00:08:41,320
He came to Shenzhen?

181
00:08:41,630 --> 00:08:42,600
When did he leave?

182
00:08:43,240 --> 00:08:45,080
He left the morning before yesterday.

183
00:08:45,550 --> 00:08:47,910
Your dad said you're strong-willed.

184
00:08:48,080 --> 00:08:49,360
(If he didn't come get you himself,)

185
00:08:49,550 --> 00:08:51,270
(you wouldn't come home for New Year.)

186
00:08:51,670 --> 00:08:52,720
Okay.

187
00:08:52,720 --> 00:08:53,790
I'll go find him right now.

188
00:09:33,480 --> 00:09:34,200
(Wanzhi,)

189
00:09:35,600 --> 00:09:37,320
(I only took two days off.)

190
00:09:39,030 --> 00:09:41,320
(I'm sorry I didn't get to see you.)

191
00:09:43,440 --> 00:09:44,910
(I suppose you plan)

192
00:09:44,910 --> 00:09:46,440
(to spend the holiday in Shenzhen.)

193
00:09:48,200 --> 00:09:50,480
(This is your first
Spring Festival away)

194
00:09:50,480 --> 00:09:51,270
(from home alone.)

195
00:09:53,030 --> 00:09:54,200
(It'll be good for you.)

196
00:09:56,630 --> 00:09:58,000
(The deal isn't over yet.)

197
00:09:59,120 --> 00:10:00,150
(I have no right)

198
00:10:00,150 --> 00:10:01,840
(to force you to resume your studies.)

199
00:10:03,960 --> 00:10:05,000
(But please remember,)

200
00:10:06,120 --> 00:10:07,440
(your home is in Yu County.)

201
00:10:08,390 --> 00:10:09,960
(You have a family who cares about you.)

202
00:10:11,480 --> 00:10:12,510
(Whenever you miss home,)

203
00:10:13,510 --> 00:10:14,600
(come back anytime.)

204
00:10:33,750 --> 00:10:34,360
(Wanzhi,)

205
00:10:35,390 --> 00:10:37,000
(why don't you come back yourself?)

206
00:10:37,840 --> 00:10:39,630
Your dad is over 50.

207
00:10:40,270 --> 00:10:40,910
The round trip

208
00:10:40,910 --> 00:10:42,200
takes dozens of hours.

209
00:10:42,200 --> 00:10:43,630
He went all the way
there to pick you up.

210
00:10:45,240 --> 00:10:46,960
Please don't break his heart.

211
00:10:50,600 --> 00:10:51,030
Your turn.

212
00:10:52,630 --> 00:10:53,200
Take it easy.

213
00:10:53,840 --> 00:10:54,790
Hello, where to?

214
00:10:54,790 --> 00:10:55,200
Nanjing.

215
00:10:55,200 --> 00:10:56,790
Nanjing? What time?

216
00:10:57,120 --> 00:10:57,670
Where to?

217
00:10:58,080 --> 00:10:58,840
Whatever is available.

218
00:10:58,870 --> 00:10:59,550
Alright.

219
00:11:00,720 --> 00:11:01,270
Where to?

220
00:11:02,200 --> 00:11:02,790
Yu County.

221
00:11:04,320 --> 00:11:04,790
One moment.

222
00:11:05,510 --> 00:11:06,510
There are no direct trains.

223
00:11:08,390 --> 00:11:09,360
Can you check

224
00:11:09,360 --> 00:11:10,200
connections?

225
00:11:10,270 --> 00:11:11,200
The earliest possible.

226
00:11:11,670 --> 00:11:12,550
No tickets before the 30th.

227
00:11:12,600 --> 00:11:13,480
Leave late on lunar Jan. 2,

228
00:11:13,600 --> 00:11:14,480
with three connections,

229
00:11:14,510 --> 00:11:15,600
arrive Yu County morning of 4th.

230
00:11:15,630 --> 00:11:16,150
Want to buy?

231
00:11:18,840 --> 00:11:19,320
Never mind.

232
00:11:20,840 --> 00:11:21,320
Where to?

233
00:11:21,320 --> 00:11:22,270
Hello, to Changsha.

234
00:11:22,510 --> 00:11:22,960
What time?

235
00:11:23,000 --> 00:11:23,550
Nine o'clock.

236
00:11:23,600 --> 00:11:24,000
Okay.

237
00:11:24,200 --> 00:11:25,270
High-paying caregiver job!

238
00:11:25,360 --> 00:11:25,910
Take a look!

239
00:11:26,600 --> 00:11:27,510
High pay!

240
00:11:27,750 --> 00:11:28,960
There's a number on it.

241
00:11:28,960 --> 00:11:30,000
Call me!

242
00:11:30,840 --> 00:11:31,720
Miss, take a look.

243
00:11:31,840 --> 00:11:33,080
Urgent hiring!

244
00:11:34,000 --> 00:11:35,270
Don't throw it away!

245
00:11:35,910 --> 00:11:37,320
High-paying caregiver job!

246
00:11:38,030 --> 00:11:39,550
Make big money during the holiday!

247
00:11:39,600 --> 00:11:40,790
High-paying caregiver job!

248
00:11:40,910 --> 00:11:42,480
High-paying caregiver job!

249
00:11:42,720 --> 00:11:43,790
High pay!

250
00:11:49,200 --> 00:11:49,720
Miss,

251
00:11:50,200 --> 00:11:51,200
you want to be a caregiver?

252
00:11:51,550 --> 00:11:52,270
The requirements?

253
00:11:55,440 --> 00:11:56,840
I wouldn't be this desperate

254
00:11:56,840 --> 00:11:58,750
if it weren't for the Spring Festival.

255
00:11:58,960 --> 00:12:00,870
The previous caregiver
was very professional,

256
00:12:00,960 --> 00:12:02,320
but she had to go home for the holiday.

257
00:12:02,720 --> 00:12:03,750
My boss told me

258
00:12:03,870 --> 00:12:05,200
that I must find someone today

259
00:12:05,270 --> 00:12:07,390
or I'll be fired.

260
00:12:07,630 --> 00:12:08,960
You're not the boss?

261
00:12:09,200 --> 00:12:10,320
How could I be?

262
00:12:10,440 --> 00:12:11,870
I'm his driver.

263
00:12:12,240 --> 00:12:12,840
Miss,

264
00:12:13,150 --> 00:12:14,080
what's your education level?

265
00:12:15,600 --> 00:12:16,670
Undergraduate.

266
00:12:18,440 --> 00:12:19,360
Undergraduate?

267
00:12:21,870 --> 00:12:23,390
I'm a bit worried.

268
00:12:24,120 --> 00:12:24,870
I'm afraid you won't

269
00:12:25,030 --> 00:12:26,440
take this job seriously.

270
00:12:27,120 --> 00:12:28,200
I didn't graduate.

271
00:12:29,000 --> 00:12:30,720
That's better.

272
00:12:30,870 --> 00:12:32,510
My boss has a rule.

273
00:12:32,840 --> 00:12:35,200
The lower the education
you have, the happier he is.

274
00:12:35,600 --> 00:12:36,320
Why?

275
00:12:36,550 --> 00:12:38,550
He only finished elementary school.

276
00:12:39,440 --> 00:12:41,030
But he's really amazing.

277
00:12:41,120 --> 00:12:42,390
I admire him a lot.

278
00:12:42,750 --> 00:12:43,320
This time,

279
00:12:43,390 --> 00:12:45,270
you'll be looking after
my boss's father.

280
00:12:45,550 --> 00:12:47,240
He had a gastrectomy

281
00:12:47,360 --> 00:12:48,550
two weeks ago.

282
00:12:48,630 --> 00:12:49,630
He can eat a little now.

283
00:12:49,870 --> 00:12:50,390
But don't worry.

284
00:12:50,480 --> 00:12:52,600
It's easier than right after surgery.

285
00:12:53,270 --> 00:12:54,200
Do you have any experience?

286
00:12:54,510 --> 00:12:55,080
No.

287
00:12:55,360 --> 00:12:56,120
No?

288
00:12:56,870 --> 00:12:58,120
Don't say that.

289
00:12:58,200 --> 00:12:59,270
If my boss asks you,

290
00:12:59,600 --> 00:13:01,000
say you do.

291
00:13:01,630 --> 00:13:03,200
Isn't that lying?

292
00:13:03,320 --> 00:13:04,870
How is it lying?

293
00:13:05,120 --> 00:13:06,150
Who hasn't

294
00:13:06,150 --> 00:13:07,870
taken care of an elder at home?

295
00:13:08,270 --> 00:13:09,080
I haven't.

296
00:13:09,120 --> 00:13:09,600
Have you...

297
00:13:10,550 --> 00:13:12,080
Have you ever helped watch any kids?

298
00:13:12,270 --> 00:13:13,360
Younger siblings perhaps?

299
00:13:13,390 --> 00:13:14,480
Or children

300
00:13:14,480 --> 00:13:16,240
of your neighbors?

301
00:13:16,510 --> 00:13:17,030
No.

302
00:13:17,270 --> 00:13:18,480
Have you ever looked after

303
00:13:18,670 --> 00:13:20,080
any cats or dogs?

304
00:13:20,910 --> 00:13:22,750
That I have.

305
00:13:23,000 --> 00:13:24,840
Then that counts.

306
00:13:24,960 --> 00:13:25,480
But...

307
00:13:26,390 --> 00:13:27,200
Think about it.

308
00:13:27,510 --> 00:13:29,390
My boss's father is a patient.

309
00:13:29,510 --> 00:13:31,630
You can just treat him like

310
00:13:31,630 --> 00:13:32,720
a cat or dog.

311
00:13:33,790 --> 00:13:35,240
You're really desperate to

312
00:13:35,240 --> 00:13:36,440
please your boss.

313
00:13:37,600 --> 00:13:38,870
I can't lie,

314
00:13:39,440 --> 00:13:40,120
so I can't

315
00:13:40,720 --> 00:13:41,670
take the job.

316
00:13:42,480 --> 00:13:43,960
Wait, wait, don't leave!

317
00:13:44,240 --> 00:13:46,120
Listen to me!

318
00:13:47,270 --> 00:13:47,910
Triple pay!

319
00:13:48,630 --> 00:13:50,240
I'll pay you triple!

320
00:13:50,870 --> 00:13:51,670
That much?

321
00:13:51,750 --> 00:13:52,390
Yes.

322
00:13:52,480 --> 00:13:54,360
It's normally 2,000 yuan a month.

323
00:13:54,510 --> 00:13:56,440
During the holiday, I'll give you 6,000!

324
00:13:56,630 --> 00:13:57,150
Look,

325
00:13:57,270 --> 00:13:59,440
from today until Lantern Festival,

326
00:13:59,600 --> 00:14:01,720
counting New Year's Eve and
New Year's Day as four days,

327
00:14:01,910 --> 00:14:03,960
it's over 20 days with
a pay of 4,000 yuan!

328
00:14:04,080 --> 00:14:05,270
If my wife didn't

329
00:14:05,390 --> 00:14:06,870
rush me home for the holiday,

330
00:14:07,000 --> 00:14:08,790
I'd take the job myself!

331
00:14:09,390 --> 00:14:10,630
You're not local?

332
00:14:10,670 --> 00:14:11,870
Nope.

333
00:14:11,870 --> 00:14:13,200
I'm from Shaanxi.

334
00:14:14,270 --> 00:14:15,480
I've been married for three years

335
00:14:15,630 --> 00:14:16,630
and had no kids.

336
00:14:16,750 --> 00:14:17,750
My wife's making me go home

337
00:14:17,750 --> 00:14:19,030
to start a family.

338
00:14:19,200 --> 00:14:19,840
Otherwise

339
00:14:19,840 --> 00:14:20,790
she'll leave me!

340
00:14:22,630 --> 00:14:23,200
Miss,

341
00:14:23,440 --> 00:14:24,750
listen to me.

342
00:14:25,360 --> 00:14:26,910
This job is great.

343
00:14:27,030 --> 00:14:28,480
You can make quick money.

344
00:14:28,720 --> 00:14:30,360
And the old man is easy to look after.

345
00:14:30,790 --> 00:14:32,910
You can just make do with it.

346
00:14:33,510 --> 00:14:34,390
How can you make do

347
00:14:34,390 --> 00:14:35,600
with it when looking after a patient?

348
00:14:37,120 --> 00:14:37,630
Fine.

349
00:14:38,030 --> 00:14:39,480
I have no experience,

350
00:14:39,720 --> 00:14:40,630
but my mom was the principal

351
00:14:40,630 --> 00:14:41,600
of a nursing school.

352
00:14:41,720 --> 00:14:42,870
I watched her work growing up.

353
00:14:43,030 --> 00:14:44,840
I believe I can do this job well.

354
00:14:45,080 --> 00:14:45,790
But under

355
00:14:45,790 --> 00:14:47,030
the terms you said,

356
00:14:47,720 --> 00:14:48,720
we need to sign a contract.

357
00:14:48,960 --> 00:14:49,510
Done.

358
00:14:50,150 --> 00:14:50,670
Okay!

359
00:15:02,840 --> 00:15:03,750
Hello, Mr. Jia.

360
00:15:04,080 --> 00:15:05,960
I'm your new caregiver, Fang.

361
00:15:06,200 --> 00:15:07,510
I'll look after you from today on.

362
00:15:16,750 --> 00:15:18,270
I need to turn you over now.

363
00:15:18,840 --> 00:15:20,120
Please cooperate with me.

364
00:15:23,440 --> 00:15:24,030
Slowly...

365
00:15:24,910 --> 00:15:25,630
That's it.

366
00:15:26,870 --> 00:15:27,910
Hold on a little longer.

367
00:15:35,030 --> 00:15:36,390
From now on, we'll do this

368
00:15:36,390 --> 00:15:37,240
three times a day

369
00:15:37,840 --> 00:15:39,270
to prevent bedsores.

370
00:15:40,630 --> 00:15:41,720
Please cooperate again.

371
00:15:42,360 --> 00:15:43,270
Let's turn

372
00:15:43,480 --> 00:15:44,150
the other side.

373
00:15:46,000 --> 00:15:46,720
Slowly.

374
00:15:47,150 --> 00:15:47,960
Great.

375
00:17:06,640 --> 00:17:07,440
Dad!

376
00:17:10,590 --> 00:17:11,590
Who are you?

377
00:17:14,000 --> 00:17:15,750
I'm the new caregiver, Fang.

378
00:17:15,880 --> 00:17:17,240
Caregiver? Instead of looking after him,

379
00:17:17,240 --> 00:17:18,550
you're sleeping on the job!

380
00:17:19,350 --> 00:17:20,510
Watch your mouth!

381
00:17:20,920 --> 00:17:21,830
Why should I?

382
00:17:22,070 --> 00:17:23,110
You dare say you weren't

383
00:17:23,110 --> 00:17:23,830
sleeping with him?

384
00:17:24,750 --> 00:17:25,750
Heh!

385
00:17:26,680 --> 00:17:29,480
Dad, I'm so sorry!

386
00:17:29,640 --> 00:17:31,350
Even the caregiver bullies you!

387
00:17:31,590 --> 00:17:32,440
She's not even working,

388
00:17:32,550 --> 00:17:34,640
and she's sleeping!

389
00:17:35,640 --> 00:17:36,510
Quiet down!

390
00:17:36,750 --> 00:17:37,590
Keep your voice low!

391
00:17:37,750 --> 00:17:38,680
The patient needs rest!

392
00:17:39,310 --> 00:17:39,790
Head nurse!

393
00:17:40,200 --> 00:17:41,110
Good timing!

394
00:17:41,440 --> 00:17:42,310
Get her out of here!

395
00:17:42,750 --> 00:17:43,440
Why?

396
00:17:44,550 --> 00:17:45,400
I'm the caregiver

397
00:17:45,400 --> 00:17:46,350
hired by Mr. Jia's family.

398
00:17:46,510 --> 00:17:47,640
I have a labor contract.

399
00:17:50,000 --> 00:17:52,510
Youcai, how can you be so careless?

400
00:17:52,510 --> 00:17:54,030
This caregiver is no good.

401
00:17:54,750 --> 00:17:55,920
You want to know why?

402
00:17:56,070 --> 00:17:57,270
She's not ugly enough.

403
00:17:57,920 --> 00:17:58,920
Didn't we agree to find

404
00:17:58,920 --> 00:18:00,480
someone much uglier than me?

405
00:18:00,790 --> 00:18:03,030
This girl's way too pretty.

406
00:18:03,350 --> 00:18:04,110
I'm afraid Dad will...

407
00:18:04,110 --> 00:18:04,960
Excuse me.

408
00:18:08,240 --> 00:18:09,200
Why aren't you inside caring

409
00:18:09,200 --> 00:18:09,750
for my dad?

410
00:18:09,750 --> 00:18:11,200
Instead, you're here eavesdropping.

411
00:18:11,590 --> 00:18:12,640
That's not my style.

412
00:18:13,550 --> 00:18:14,510
Mr. Jia's asking for you.

413
00:18:18,000 --> 00:18:19,240
I'll call you back, Youcai.

414
00:18:26,310 --> 00:18:27,440
Dad,

415
00:18:28,550 --> 00:18:29,070
what's wrong?

416
00:18:37,070 --> 00:18:38,590
You only had surgery.

417
00:18:38,590 --> 00:18:40,400
How come you can't talk now?

418
00:18:41,640 --> 00:18:43,000
His slurred speech is

419
00:18:43,000 --> 00:18:44,680
from an electrolyte imbalance

420
00:18:44,680 --> 00:18:45,790
after the tube was removed.

421
00:18:46,110 --> 00:18:46,920
Doctors have arranged

422
00:18:46,920 --> 00:18:47,680
recovery treatment.

423
00:18:47,830 --> 00:18:48,480
It will be better

424
00:18:48,480 --> 00:18:49,240
in a few days.

425
00:18:54,350 --> 00:18:55,110
Dad, what is it?

426
00:18:55,110 --> 00:18:56,350
I can't understand a word.

427
00:18:58,030 --> 00:18:58,720
Mr. Jia,

428
00:18:59,030 --> 00:19:00,200
are you trying to say

429
00:19:00,310 --> 00:19:01,790
you want her to go
to her in-laws' place?

430
00:19:04,920 --> 00:19:06,110
My mother-in-law can't cook.

431
00:19:06,110 --> 00:19:07,510
I'd have to cook for her.

432
00:19:07,750 --> 00:19:08,590
I'm not going.

433
00:19:09,350 --> 00:19:10,030
Dad,

434
00:19:11,070 --> 00:19:12,400
you just had a surgery.

435
00:19:12,680 --> 00:19:13,750
As your daughter,

436
00:19:13,750 --> 00:19:15,350
I should stay with you every day.

437
00:19:17,510 --> 00:19:18,400
Tell her to leave.

438
00:19:18,400 --> 00:19:19,790
Let me take care of you, okay, Dad?

439
00:19:25,680 --> 00:19:26,640
What's he saying now?

440
00:19:27,590 --> 00:19:29,550
He says he'd love to have you here,

441
00:19:29,640 --> 00:19:31,240
but he doesn't want to burden you.

442
00:19:31,680 --> 00:19:32,880
He wants us to work together.

443
00:19:34,310 --> 00:19:35,640
I can't even understand

444
00:19:36,240 --> 00:19:37,720
what my dad is saying.

445
00:19:37,720 --> 00:19:38,750
How do you know?

446
00:19:39,070 --> 00:19:40,510
Because you're not listening carefully.

447
00:19:40,790 --> 00:19:41,790
Bullshit!

448
00:19:41,880 --> 00:19:42,830
Stop yelling!

449
00:19:43,030 --> 00:19:44,400
This is a hospital. Keep it down!

450
00:19:44,510 --> 00:19:45,030
You...

451
00:19:47,640 --> 00:19:48,440
Just you wait.

452
00:19:49,000 --> 00:19:50,070
You'll pay for this!

453
00:20:17,310 --> 00:20:18,160
Dad!

454
00:20:20,240 --> 00:20:21,440
Why are you hitting my dad?

455
00:20:22,200 --> 00:20:23,030
You've misunderstood me.

456
00:20:23,240 --> 00:20:24,070
How can I misunderstand?

457
00:20:24,070 --> 00:20:24,680
You made

458
00:20:24,680 --> 00:20:26,270
my dad cry!

459
00:20:26,640 --> 00:20:27,200
Get away!

460
00:20:28,000 --> 00:20:28,880
Dad, are you okay?

461
00:20:29,550 --> 00:20:30,880
This isn't care!

462
00:20:31,680 --> 00:20:32,440
This is outright

463
00:20:32,440 --> 00:20:33,310
torture and abuse!

464
00:20:36,400 --> 00:20:37,440
It's Lunar New Year's Eve,

465
00:20:37,440 --> 00:20:38,920
and this is all you're feeding him?

466
00:20:39,680 --> 00:20:40,030
Dad,

467
00:20:40,030 --> 00:20:41,160
you can't rely on strangers.

468
00:20:41,350 --> 00:20:42,030
Look what I

469
00:20:42,030 --> 00:20:42,750
brought you.

470
00:20:46,960 --> 00:20:48,440
There are your favorite clay pot rice,

471
00:20:49,240 --> 00:20:50,440
bamboo shoots with quail eggs,

472
00:20:51,160 --> 00:20:53,270
and steamed sea bass.

473
00:20:53,440 --> 00:20:54,680
I'll open it for you, Dad.

474
00:20:54,920 --> 00:20:56,200
He's still in recovery.

475
00:20:56,200 --> 00:20:57,750
He can only have liquid food right now.

476
00:20:58,160 --> 00:20:59,350
Does this fill him up?

477
00:20:59,640 --> 00:21:00,440
To keep him full,

478
00:21:00,480 --> 00:21:02,270
I make sure Mr. Jia
eats five meals a day.

479
00:21:03,200 --> 00:21:04,350
Even eight meals

480
00:21:04,350 --> 00:21:05,240
of just porridge

481
00:21:05,240 --> 00:21:06,030
won't fill him!

482
00:21:06,270 --> 00:21:07,350
If you're feeding him porridge,

483
00:21:07,350 --> 00:21:09,000
at least put some lobster in it!

484
00:21:09,400 --> 00:21:10,640
It's Lunar New Year's Eve!

485
00:21:10,920 --> 00:21:12,110
Look how thin he is!

486
00:21:18,510 --> 00:21:19,590
Have some milk, Dad.

487
00:21:19,680 --> 00:21:20,640
He can't have milk.

488
00:21:21,000 --> 00:21:21,880
After a gastrectomy,

489
00:21:21,880 --> 00:21:22,920
his stomach capacity is reduced

490
00:21:23,030 --> 00:21:24,000
and his digestion speeds up.

491
00:21:24,200 --> 00:21:25,310
Milk will cause bloating

492
00:21:25,310 --> 00:21:26,110
and stomach pain.

493
00:21:27,070 --> 00:21:27,960
Are you a doctor?

494
00:21:29,400 --> 00:21:30,240
Get out!

495
00:21:30,350 --> 00:21:31,240
This is a hospital.

496
00:21:31,550 --> 00:21:32,550
What's all that noise?

497
00:21:32,880 --> 00:21:33,400
Head nurse,

498
00:21:33,400 --> 00:21:34,640
I'm glad you came!

499
00:21:35,030 --> 00:21:35,920
Talk some sense to her!

500
00:21:35,920 --> 00:21:36,790
She knows nothing

501
00:21:36,790 --> 00:21:37,920
and she's abusing my dad!

502
00:21:39,310 --> 00:21:40,070
I heard everything

503
00:21:40,070 --> 00:21:40,790
Fang just said.

504
00:21:41,110 --> 00:21:42,110
She's really professional.

505
00:21:42,590 --> 00:21:43,720
At this stage, the patient

506
00:21:43,790 --> 00:21:45,000
truly cannot have milk.

507
00:21:45,960 --> 00:21:46,920
I don't care!

508
00:21:47,640 --> 00:21:48,400
I saw her hit

509
00:21:48,400 --> 00:21:49,480
my dad with my own eyes!

510
00:21:50,000 --> 00:21:51,200
Mr. Jia just choked.

511
00:21:51,510 --> 00:21:52,400
I was patting his back.

512
00:21:53,350 --> 00:21:54,110
Patting a choking

513
00:21:54,110 --> 00:21:55,240
patient is routine.

514
00:21:55,240 --> 00:21:56,310
How is that hitting?

515
00:21:56,550 --> 00:21:57,790
Anyone can do it,

516
00:21:57,790 --> 00:21:58,880
but she can't

517
00:21:58,880 --> 00:21:59,790
take care of my dad!

518
00:22:00,480 --> 00:22:01,160
Why?

519
00:22:02,310 --> 00:22:03,310
She's too pretty!

520
00:22:03,790 --> 00:22:05,200
She's like a flirt!

521
00:22:06,000 --> 00:22:08,200
Look how gorgeous she is!

522
00:22:08,200 --> 00:22:09,240
She's only here

523
00:22:09,480 --> 00:22:10,550
because our family is rich!

524
00:22:10,550 --> 00:22:11,510
She's trying to seduce Dad!

525
00:22:11,550 --> 00:22:12,790
What are you talking about?

526
00:22:12,920 --> 00:22:14,000
Don't you dare glare at me!

527
00:22:14,590 --> 00:22:15,400
Seeing you makes me

528
00:22:15,400 --> 00:22:16,480
want to slap you!

529
00:22:16,510 --> 00:22:17,640
You want to slap me?

530
00:22:17,720 --> 00:22:18,350
If you dare to

531
00:22:18,350 --> 00:22:19,200
lay a finger on me,

532
00:22:19,200 --> 00:22:20,030
I'll call the police!

533
00:22:20,160 --> 00:22:21,240
You wanna pick a fight?

534
00:22:21,270 --> 00:22:22,510
You want to fight me?

535
00:22:22,550 --> 00:22:24,160
Enough! Stop fighting!

536
00:22:24,960 --> 00:22:25,590
Ms. Jia,

537
00:22:26,160 --> 00:22:27,550
you're way out of line.

538
00:22:28,240 --> 00:22:29,440
It's Spring Festival.

539
00:22:29,440 --> 00:22:30,590
Caregivers are in short supply.

540
00:22:30,680 --> 00:22:32,000
You should be grateful to have

541
00:22:32,030 --> 00:22:32,880
someone like Fang.

542
00:22:33,030 --> 00:22:33,680
Shenzhen is so big.

543
00:22:33,680 --> 00:22:35,310
Can't I find someone else?

544
00:22:36,640 --> 00:22:37,510
Fang!

545
00:22:38,200 --> 00:22:40,720
You are fired!

546
00:22:41,400 --> 00:22:42,350
Get out of here right now!

547
00:22:44,000 --> 00:22:45,070
I quit!

548
00:22:46,030 --> 00:22:47,310
Pay me my three days' wages.

549
00:22:47,550 --> 00:22:48,720
What? You worked a day and a half,

550
00:22:48,720 --> 00:22:49,790
and you want three days' pay?

551
00:22:49,790 --> 00:22:51,240
It's written in the contract.

552
00:22:51,240 --> 00:22:52,000
Read it yourself.

553
00:22:52,270 --> 00:22:54,160
I didn't sign the contract.
I don't recognize it!

554
00:22:54,480 --> 00:22:55,000
Get out!

555
00:22:57,720 --> 00:22:58,920
I don't want to argue here,

556
00:22:59,240 --> 00:23:00,000
but I will defend

557
00:23:00,000 --> 00:23:00,920
my rights.

558
00:23:06,030 --> 00:23:06,510
Dad!

559
00:23:07,110 --> 00:23:08,070
Dad, are you okay? Dad!

560
00:23:08,440 --> 00:23:09,030
Fang!

561
00:23:09,880 --> 00:23:10,830
Fang, wait!

562
00:23:15,510 --> 00:23:17,160
I noticed you from the start.

563
00:23:17,440 --> 00:23:19,200
You're diligent and professional.

564
00:23:20,070 --> 00:23:21,350
Our department needs caregivers.

565
00:23:21,640 --> 00:23:22,640
Why don't you stay?

566
00:23:23,000 --> 00:23:24,030
The department will pay you.

567
00:23:24,240 --> 00:23:25,550
We can sign a long-term contract.

568
00:23:26,680 --> 00:23:27,590
Thank you, Head Nurse.

569
00:23:28,790 --> 00:23:30,030
I'm not professionally trained.

570
00:23:30,440 --> 00:23:31,880
This job isn't right for me.

571
00:23:32,830 --> 00:23:33,480
Fang,

572
00:23:34,070 --> 00:23:34,680
it's normal to

573
00:23:34,680 --> 00:23:36,200
have feelings hurt in this job.

574
00:23:36,680 --> 00:23:37,400
Don't just

575
00:23:37,550 --> 00:23:38,750
give up so easily.

576
00:23:39,110 --> 00:23:39,510
No.

577
00:23:40,000 --> 00:23:41,200
I never planned to work

578
00:23:41,200 --> 00:23:42,350
in a hospital long-term.

579
00:23:42,920 --> 00:23:43,550
I just wanted

580
00:23:43,960 --> 00:23:45,480
to earn some money during

581
00:23:45,720 --> 00:23:46,350
the holiday.

582
00:23:47,720 --> 00:23:48,750
Thank you for the offer.

583
00:24:07,920 --> 00:24:08,550
Who is it?

584
00:24:12,510 --> 00:24:14,240
Are you Ms. Fang?

585
00:24:14,880 --> 00:24:15,680
You are...

586
00:24:16,030 --> 00:24:17,110
I'm Jia Youcai,

587
00:24:17,440 --> 00:24:19,160
Jia Zhihuai's son.

588
00:24:21,240 --> 00:24:22,550
You must be lying.

589
00:24:22,720 --> 00:24:24,310
Why would I lie to you?

590
00:24:27,350 --> 00:24:28,030
Ms. Fang,

591
00:24:28,590 --> 00:24:29,590
this is my ID.

592
00:24:29,720 --> 00:24:30,400
Take a look.

593
00:24:35,310 --> 00:24:36,640
You really are Boss Jia.

594
00:24:37,440 --> 00:24:39,000
No need to call me a boss.

595
00:24:39,270 --> 00:24:40,440
Just call me Youcai.

596
00:24:42,920 --> 00:24:43,750
Come in, please.

597
00:24:44,310 --> 00:24:45,270
Thank you, Ms. Fang.

598
00:24:52,000 --> 00:24:52,920
Thank you.

599
00:24:58,440 --> 00:25:01,000
Your driver is in a suit,
but you're not.

600
00:25:03,550 --> 00:25:04,880
He likes dressing up.

601
00:25:05,510 --> 00:25:07,310
I just feel

602
00:25:07,310 --> 00:25:09,000
uncomfortable in a suit.

603
00:25:09,680 --> 00:25:11,830
Besides, I'm still working.

604
00:25:12,000 --> 00:25:13,480
I came straight over.

605
00:25:14,110 --> 00:25:15,590
Luckily the contract has your address.

606
00:25:15,830 --> 00:25:17,440
I'd be in trouble

607
00:25:17,440 --> 00:25:18,350
if I couldn't find you.

608
00:25:18,720 --> 00:25:19,720
So why are you here?

609
00:25:20,240 --> 00:25:20,680
It's not

610
00:25:20,680 --> 00:25:21,680
about my pay, is it?

611
00:25:22,070 --> 00:25:23,000
Exactly!

612
00:25:23,830 --> 00:25:24,480
Ms. Fang,

613
00:25:26,160 --> 00:25:27,480
here's 4,000 yuan.

614
00:25:27,590 --> 00:25:28,960
Your full salary.

615
00:25:30,160 --> 00:25:31,480
I only worked a day and a half.

616
00:25:31,880 --> 00:25:32,440
Per the contract,

617
00:25:32,440 --> 00:25:33,680
you fired me unilaterally.

618
00:25:33,830 --> 00:25:35,350
You only owe me three days' pay.

619
00:25:35,480 --> 00:25:36,350
That's 600 yuan.

620
00:25:39,310 --> 00:25:41,680
I'm here to ask you to come back.

621
00:25:43,350 --> 00:25:44,270
But your sister

622
00:25:44,270 --> 00:25:45,680
already fired me.

623
00:25:46,000 --> 00:25:47,510
Don't mention her!

624
00:25:48,030 --> 00:25:49,830
She said she'd take care of Dad,

625
00:25:50,240 --> 00:25:51,640
but she couldn't even last

626
00:25:51,640 --> 00:25:52,680
two hours.

627
00:25:53,160 --> 00:25:54,480
She left already.

628
00:25:55,750 --> 00:25:56,550
Ms. Fang,

629
00:25:57,350 --> 00:25:58,750
today's Lunar New Year's Eve.

630
00:25:59,240 --> 00:25:59,960
I really

631
00:26:00,400 --> 00:26:01,720
shouldn't be here.

632
00:26:02,110 --> 00:26:03,590
I should be home

633
00:26:03,590 --> 00:26:04,680
with my dad.

634
00:26:05,440 --> 00:26:07,440
But I'm stuck at work.

635
00:26:07,440 --> 00:26:08,750
I can't get away.

636
00:26:09,790 --> 00:26:10,510
Ms. Fang,

637
00:26:10,830 --> 00:26:12,000
please let bygones be bygones

638
00:26:12,550 --> 00:26:13,960
and help me out, okay?

639
00:26:18,590 --> 00:26:19,240
Ms. Fang,

640
00:26:20,750 --> 00:26:21,480
I sincerely

641
00:26:21,480 --> 00:26:22,680
apologize for my

642
00:26:22,830 --> 00:26:23,920
unreasonable sister.

643
00:26:24,240 --> 00:26:24,830
I promise

644
00:26:25,070 --> 00:26:25,960
she won't come to

645
00:26:25,960 --> 00:26:27,000
bother you again.

646
00:26:27,270 --> 00:26:28,000
Ms. Fang,

647
00:26:28,480 --> 00:26:29,350
I'm sorry.

648
00:26:32,400 --> 00:26:33,830
I'm really sorry, Ms. Fang.

649
00:26:36,920 --> 00:26:37,480
Fine.

650
00:26:40,070 --> 00:26:41,550
But I can't take the money.

651
00:26:41,920 --> 00:26:43,270
I should get paid only after

652
00:26:43,270 --> 00:26:43,880
I finish the work.

653
00:26:44,310 --> 00:26:45,200
You agree?

654
00:26:45,440 --> 00:26:46,200
Let's go!

655
00:26:46,510 --> 00:26:47,960
I'll drive you to the hospital!

656
00:26:48,240 --> 00:26:48,720
No, it's okay.

657
00:26:49,030 --> 00:26:50,200
Don't worry.

658
00:26:50,590 --> 00:26:51,750
My car is nice,

659
00:26:51,920 --> 00:26:53,200
big, and clean.

660
00:26:53,270 --> 00:26:53,920
Really, no need.

661
00:26:54,400 --> 00:26:55,750
I'll get to the hospital soon.

662
00:26:57,590 --> 00:26:58,350
Alright.

663
00:26:59,640 --> 00:27:00,830
Just come when you're ready.

664
00:27:01,270 --> 00:27:03,200
You can ride my car another time.

665
00:27:04,440 --> 00:27:05,680
It's Lunar New Year's Eve.

666
00:27:05,880 --> 00:27:06,880
I ordered a New Year dinner.

667
00:27:07,350 --> 00:27:08,720
It'll be delivered to the ward.

668
00:27:09,310 --> 00:27:10,880
Mr. Jia can't have that.

669
00:27:10,920 --> 00:27:12,160
He can only have liquids.

670
00:27:12,480 --> 00:27:14,160
It's for you, Ms. Fang.

671
00:27:14,440 --> 00:27:15,480
Just a simple meal.

672
00:27:15,920 --> 00:27:16,880
I can't accept free gifts.

673
00:27:17,310 --> 00:27:18,550
And I don't like eating a big meal

674
00:27:18,550 --> 00:27:19,350
in the ward.

675
00:27:20,680 --> 00:27:21,480
Okay.

676
00:27:22,400 --> 00:27:24,640
I'll call them

677
00:27:24,640 --> 00:27:25,480
to cancel it.

678
00:27:25,960 --> 00:27:27,640
It'll be too late soon.

679
00:27:29,240 --> 00:27:29,790
Mr. Jia!

680
00:27:32,590 --> 00:27:33,750
Thank you, Ms. Fang.

681
00:27:34,070 --> 00:27:34,720
Thank you.

682
00:27:35,240 --> 00:27:37,030
I have to go now.

683
00:27:38,440 --> 00:27:39,960
I'll leave Dad in your care.

684
00:27:40,310 --> 00:27:41,400
Bye, Ms. Fang.

685
00:27:41,920 --> 00:27:42,590
Drive safe.

686
00:28:06,750 --> 00:28:08,350
Why are you coughing, Mr. Jia?

687
00:29:10,920 --> 00:29:11,880
It went into his lung.

688
00:29:12,510 --> 00:29:13,400
Good thing she noticed.

689
00:29:14,030 --> 00:29:15,200
Or, it could cause an infection and

690
00:29:15,200 --> 00:29:15,720
become serious.

691
00:29:15,920 --> 00:29:16,920
Suction immediately.

692
00:29:20,640 --> 00:29:21,110
Fang,

693
00:29:21,920 --> 00:29:23,350
the patient isn't
completely out of danger.

694
00:29:23,480 --> 00:29:24,200
Notify us right away

695
00:29:24,310 --> 00:29:25,000
if anything happens.

696
00:30:54,070 --> 00:30:54,830
Grandma Yu.

697
00:30:57,440 --> 00:30:58,200
You're back.

698
00:31:02,270 --> 00:31:03,550
I'm sorry, Grandma Yu.

699
00:31:05,030 --> 00:31:05,640
I failed

700
00:31:05,640 --> 00:31:06,880
the task you entrusted me with.

701
00:31:07,960 --> 00:31:08,790
I didn't

702
00:31:10,030 --> 00:31:10,830
find Wanzhi.

703
00:31:11,510 --> 00:31:12,640
She called.

704
00:31:13,070 --> 00:31:13,880
When?

705
00:31:14,310 --> 00:31:14,920
Yesterday.

706
00:31:15,160 --> 00:31:16,070
Twice.

707
00:31:16,160 --> 00:31:16,960
What did she say?

708
00:31:17,310 --> 00:31:18,680
I told her to come home for the holiday,

709
00:31:19,830 --> 00:31:22,310
but she hesitated and wouldn't agree.

710
00:31:24,270 --> 00:31:25,400
She called...

711
00:31:27,160 --> 00:31:28,680
That's good to hear.

712
00:31:30,200 --> 00:31:31,070
It means she still cares

713
00:31:31,070 --> 00:31:32,030
about us.

714
00:31:32,310 --> 00:31:33,240
Yes.

715
00:31:34,400 --> 00:31:35,640
Good.

716
00:31:36,480 --> 00:31:38,720
Let's have New Year's Eve dinner.

717
00:31:39,440 --> 00:31:40,640
I made a few dishes.

718
00:31:41,110 --> 00:31:41,640
Okay.

719
00:31:44,350 --> 00:31:45,830
Mom, try the dumplings.

720
00:31:53,880 --> 00:31:54,720
Good.

721
00:31:55,070 --> 00:31:55,830
It's delicious.

722
00:31:58,680 --> 00:32:00,000
Shuchun has some too.

723
00:32:03,680 --> 00:32:05,160
I served him a plate.

724
00:32:13,110 --> 00:32:13,920
Juan,

725
00:32:15,000 --> 00:32:16,200
I don't mean to scold you,

726
00:32:17,310 --> 00:32:18,270
but it's New Year's Eve.

727
00:32:19,070 --> 00:32:20,270
Think something good.

728
00:32:21,590 --> 00:32:24,240
Seeing us happy,

729
00:32:25,270 --> 00:32:26,720
Shuchun will rest in peace.

730
00:32:30,590 --> 00:32:31,350
Let's eat.

731
00:33:07,830 --> 00:33:08,440
Hey.

732
00:33:14,400 --> 00:33:15,240
Open it for me.

733
00:33:19,030 --> 00:33:20,000
Give it to me!

734
00:33:21,350 --> 00:33:22,030
What's wrong?

735
00:33:22,960 --> 00:33:24,750
Your family is really something.

736
00:33:25,070 --> 00:33:25,680
The men

737
00:33:26,350 --> 00:33:28,270
can drink and play games

738
00:33:28,480 --> 00:33:29,400
and yell all they want,

739
00:33:29,480 --> 00:33:30,920
but the women can't even drink?

740
00:33:30,920 --> 00:33:31,590
Why?

741
00:33:32,720 --> 00:33:34,000
We have rules.

742
00:33:34,590 --> 00:33:35,720
Women don't drink.

743
00:33:36,480 --> 00:33:37,590
But you know perfectly

744
00:33:37,590 --> 00:33:38,680
well I can drink.

745
00:33:38,750 --> 00:33:39,750
But you're marrying

746
00:33:40,110 --> 00:33:41,590
into my family now.

747
00:33:45,350 --> 00:33:47,830
You need to get rid of that bad habit.

748
00:33:48,000 --> 00:33:49,590
Who are you saying has a bad habit?

749
00:33:50,000 --> 00:33:50,640
Why can't you

750
00:33:50,640 --> 00:33:51,400
change the rules?

751
00:33:52,790 --> 00:33:53,880
Buy me a ticket right now.

752
00:33:53,920 --> 00:33:55,110
I'm going back to Shenzhen!

753
00:33:55,110 --> 00:33:56,240
Fine, fine, Qian.

754
00:33:56,790 --> 00:33:57,830
How can you leave?

755
00:33:58,270 --> 00:33:59,590
The wedding isn't over yet.

756
00:33:59,920 --> 00:34:01,030
We'll have the banquet from

757
00:34:01,030 --> 00:34:02,510
lunar Jan. 2 till Jan. 6!

758
00:34:03,270 --> 00:34:04,960
That's your family's feast.

759
00:34:05,110 --> 00:34:06,110
What's that to me?

760
00:34:06,440 --> 00:34:07,880
We're getting married.

761
00:34:08,280 --> 00:34:09,670
How is it not to you?

762
00:34:10,760 --> 00:34:12,070
I just want to know.

763
00:34:12,360 --> 00:34:14,710
Can this rule be changed or not?

764
00:34:14,800 --> 00:34:15,280
Yes!

765
00:34:16,480 --> 00:34:17,110
We'll change it!

766
00:34:17,760 --> 00:34:18,880
We'll change it, okay?

767
00:34:21,920 --> 00:34:22,670
There's no food.

768
00:34:24,000 --> 00:34:24,630
Yes, there is!

769
00:34:32,070 --> 00:34:34,000
I'm starving.

770
00:34:39,630 --> 00:34:40,190
Here.

771
00:34:41,630 --> 00:34:42,440
What now?

772
00:34:42,760 --> 00:34:44,000
You know I can't drink right now.

773
00:34:46,840 --> 00:34:48,110
I'm just angry.

774
00:34:48,280 --> 00:34:49,150
But to be clear,

775
00:34:49,550 --> 00:34:51,400
you listen to me from now on.

776
00:35:05,710 --> 00:35:06,400
Mr. Jia,

777
00:35:07,440 --> 00:35:08,150
time to eat.

778
00:35:08,840 --> 00:35:09,360
Fang,

779
00:35:09,760 --> 00:35:10,840
what am I having today?

780
00:35:11,840 --> 00:35:13,710
The doctor says you're recovering well.

781
00:35:13,960 --> 00:35:15,760
You can have a sweet dumpling today.

782
00:35:16,230 --> 00:35:16,880
Sweet dumpling?

783
00:35:17,710 --> 00:35:18,150
So

784
00:35:19,360 --> 00:35:20,630
can I have a few more?

785
00:35:21,280 --> 00:35:21,960
No.

786
00:35:23,400 --> 00:35:25,150
Today is Lantern Festival.

787
00:35:25,440 --> 00:35:26,960
That's why you can get a sweet dumpling.

788
00:35:28,710 --> 00:35:29,760
Only one.

789
00:35:31,400 --> 00:35:32,480
When you're fully recovered,

790
00:35:32,550 --> 00:35:34,150
you can eat as many as you like.

791
00:35:34,760 --> 00:35:35,760
Here, drink the soup first.

792
00:35:36,190 --> 00:35:36,590
Okay.

793
00:35:37,800 --> 00:35:38,710
You sit as well.

794
00:35:47,030 --> 00:35:48,480
When the director did rounds today,

795
00:35:49,230 --> 00:35:50,880
he said if you hadn't
noticed the foreign

796
00:35:51,190 --> 00:35:52,070
object in my bronchus,

797
00:35:52,280 --> 00:35:53,280
I'd have been in danger.

798
00:35:54,070 --> 00:35:55,480
Thanks to you, Ms. Fang,

799
00:35:55,800 --> 00:35:56,920
I survived

800
00:35:57,030 --> 00:35:57,840
this incident.

801
00:35:58,150 --> 00:35:59,550
You're welcome, sir.

802
00:36:00,190 --> 00:36:01,280
It's my job.

803
00:36:04,440 --> 00:36:05,760
The head nurse just said

804
00:36:06,150 --> 00:36:07,550
your previous caregiver

805
00:36:07,590 --> 00:36:08,400
is back.

806
00:36:08,510 --> 00:36:09,920
She can start tonight.

807
00:36:10,400 --> 00:36:11,800
My contract

808
00:36:11,920 --> 00:36:12,960
also ends today.

809
00:36:17,840 --> 00:36:19,190
Can you stay?

810
00:36:20,800 --> 00:36:21,800
Even after I'm discharged,

811
00:36:21,800 --> 00:36:22,920
I still need care.

812
00:36:23,440 --> 00:36:24,230
I'll tell my son

813
00:36:24,630 --> 00:36:26,190
to keep paying you triple.

814
00:36:28,480 --> 00:36:29,880
That's kind of you, Mr. Jia.

815
00:36:31,480 --> 00:36:33,110
But I'm not a professional caregiver.

816
00:36:34,030 --> 00:36:35,440
And I came to Shenzhen

817
00:36:36,000 --> 00:36:37,400
to build a career.

818
00:36:38,630 --> 00:36:39,550
Please be understanding.

819
00:36:48,960 --> 00:36:50,000
Fang,

820
00:36:53,440 --> 00:36:55,550
I really don't want you to leave.

821
00:37:20,440 --> 00:37:21,400
Hello?

822
00:37:22,710 --> 00:37:23,280
(Hello?)

823
00:37:24,590 --> 00:37:25,550
It's Wanzhi.

824
00:37:27,760 --> 00:37:29,110
(I'd like to wish you)

825
00:37:29,630 --> 00:37:30,480
(a happy Lunar New Year.)

826
00:37:32,070 --> 00:37:33,280
Happy new year to you too.

827
00:37:34,360 --> 00:37:36,630
What are you doing now?

828
00:37:36,880 --> 00:37:37,920
Is everything okay?

829
00:37:38,550 --> 00:37:39,440
Is that Wanzhi?

830
00:37:39,960 --> 00:37:41,800
Talk to Grandma Yu first.

831
00:37:44,030 --> 00:37:45,630
Grandma, happy Lunar New Year!

832
00:37:46,230 --> 00:37:47,480
(Thank you.)

833
00:37:47,800 --> 00:37:49,360
How are you doing, Wanzhi?

834
00:37:49,880 --> 00:37:51,150
I miss you.

835
00:37:53,030 --> 00:37:54,360
(I won't take up too much of your time.)

836
00:37:54,710 --> 00:37:55,840
You can talk to your dad.

837
00:37:57,710 --> 00:37:58,480
Wanzhi,

838
00:37:59,030 --> 00:37:59,880
during Spring Festival,

839
00:37:59,880 --> 00:38:01,110
I spoke with the school.

840
00:38:01,360 --> 00:38:02,800
(They said if you come back when)

841
00:38:02,840 --> 00:38:03,710
(the semester starts)

842
00:38:03,760 --> 00:38:04,920
(and catch up with your classes,)

843
00:38:05,150 --> 00:38:06,480
you'll be able to graduate

844
00:38:06,480 --> 00:38:07,280
with your class

845
00:38:07,710 --> 00:38:08,960
and get your degree.

846
00:38:11,800 --> 00:38:12,670
Thank you.

847
00:38:13,880 --> 00:38:15,510
I still want to stay in Shenzhen.

848
00:38:16,030 --> 00:38:17,670
(I've already found a new job.)

849
00:38:18,150 --> 00:38:20,670
(The working environment and pay)

850
00:38:21,030 --> 00:38:22,320
(are much better than before.)

851
00:38:22,670 --> 00:38:23,510
(Don't worry.)

852
00:38:23,840 --> 00:38:24,840
(The reason I called so late)

853
00:38:24,840 --> 00:38:26,110
(to wish you a happy new year)

854
00:38:26,230 --> 00:38:27,710
is because I've been working

855
00:38:27,710 --> 00:38:28,880
the entire holiday.

856
00:38:29,190 --> 00:38:30,440
In Shenzhen,

857
00:38:31,320 --> 00:38:32,440
holiday overtime pay

858
00:38:32,440 --> 00:38:33,710
is double or triple.

859
00:38:34,550 --> 00:38:35,230
Wanzhi,

860
00:38:35,440 --> 00:38:36,320
that rule...

861
00:38:37,070 --> 00:38:38,190
is really good.

862
00:38:38,190 --> 00:38:39,280
We could learn from that.

863
00:38:39,920 --> 00:38:41,320
But if you're working overtime,

864
00:38:41,320 --> 00:38:42,510
you must take care of yourself.

865
00:38:47,550 --> 00:38:48,840
I wish you good health

866
00:38:49,360 --> 00:38:50,280
and all the best.

867
00:38:50,710 --> 00:38:51,190
(Wait,)

868
00:38:51,360 --> 00:38:52,030
(wait, Wanzhi!)

869
00:38:52,440 --> 00:38:54,070
If you have

870
00:38:54,480 --> 00:38:55,150
a new number

871
00:38:55,150 --> 00:38:56,110
or address,

872
00:38:56,760 --> 00:38:58,190
let us know.

873
00:38:59,360 --> 00:38:59,880
Okay.

874
00:39:00,800 --> 00:39:01,440
I'm hanging up.

875
00:39:02,320 --> 00:39:02,760
(Okay.)

876
00:39:27,190 --> 00:39:28,360
Hello, Ms. Fang.

877
00:39:32,590 --> 00:39:33,800
It's me!

878
00:39:36,280 --> 00:39:37,230
Oh, it's you.

879
00:39:37,400 --> 00:39:38,230
Yes, me.

880
00:39:39,320 --> 00:39:40,110
Ms. Fang,

881
00:39:41,190 --> 00:39:42,480
this is your pay.

882
00:39:43,070 --> 00:39:43,760
Thank you.

883
00:39:44,440 --> 00:39:46,150
These are for you.

884
00:39:47,440 --> 00:39:48,230
Thank you so much.

885
00:39:49,320 --> 00:39:50,110
Ms. Fang,

886
00:39:50,670 --> 00:39:52,360
you took such good care

887
00:39:52,590 --> 00:39:54,110
of my dad.

888
00:39:55,070 --> 00:39:56,760
I really appreciate it.

889
00:39:57,360 --> 00:39:59,030
You're too kind, Mr. Jia.

890
00:39:59,590 --> 00:40:01,000
Please don't call me that.

891
00:40:01,110 --> 00:40:02,480
Call me Youcai.

892
00:40:02,630 --> 00:40:04,400
No need to be so formal.

893
00:40:05,280 --> 00:40:07,400
I'm not used to that.

894
00:40:07,800 --> 00:40:09,710
You'll get used to it.

895
00:40:10,440 --> 00:40:11,440
Can I

896
00:40:11,590 --> 00:40:14,030
treat you to a cup of tea?

897
00:40:15,000 --> 00:40:16,800
That's kind of you, Mr. Jia.

898
00:40:17,070 --> 00:40:19,360
I already had morning tea.

899
00:40:20,550 --> 00:40:21,480
That's okay.

900
00:40:21,840 --> 00:40:22,550
I'll wait to have

901
00:40:22,550 --> 00:40:23,920
a late-night snack with you.

902
00:40:24,480 --> 00:40:25,550
You're a busy man.

903
00:40:25,880 --> 00:40:27,030
It's really not necessary.

904
00:40:27,150 --> 00:40:28,760
How is this not necessary?

905
00:40:29,190 --> 00:40:31,000
A meal is the least I can do.

906
00:40:31,710 --> 00:40:32,320
Besides,

907
00:40:32,400 --> 00:40:33,800
you still haven't ridden in my car.

908
00:40:34,190 --> 00:40:36,030
It's big and clean.

909
00:40:36,920 --> 00:40:37,550
Also,

910
00:40:37,550 --> 00:40:39,030
my dad specifically told me

911
00:40:39,400 --> 00:40:41,510
to thank you properly.

912
00:40:45,480 --> 00:40:46,190
Alright then.

913
00:40:46,550 --> 00:40:47,550
Please wait a moment.

914
00:40:47,710 --> 00:40:48,510
Alright, sure.

915
00:40:48,590 --> 00:40:49,190
I'll wait.

916
00:40:49,360 --> 00:40:50,000
No rush.

917
00:40:50,000 --> 00:40:51,110
I'll wait as long as needed.

918
00:40:51,440 --> 00:40:52,590
Okay, just a minute.

919
00:40:53,000 --> 00:40:53,760
No rush at all.

920
00:41:02,360 --> 00:41:03,030
Ms. Fang,

921
00:41:03,710 --> 00:41:05,070
that's my car.

922
00:41:08,590 --> 00:41:09,670
You can sit

923
00:41:09,670 --> 00:41:10,880
anywhere inside.

924
00:41:12,480 --> 00:41:13,480
It really is big

925
00:41:13,920 --> 00:41:14,670
and clean.

926
00:41:15,070 --> 00:41:16,550
I don't brag.

927
00:41:17,230 --> 00:41:17,920
Please get in.

928
00:41:37,670 --> 00:41:38,400
Ms. Fang,

929
00:41:39,400 --> 00:41:41,840
isn't this nice?

930
00:41:44,590 --> 00:41:45,800
I don't like cars.

931
00:41:46,110 --> 00:41:47,480
I only like buses.

932
00:41:48,070 --> 00:41:49,000
Look at the view.

933
00:41:49,590 --> 00:41:50,840
Isn't it great?

934
00:41:51,320 --> 00:41:52,190
Don't you feel

935
00:41:52,400 --> 00:41:54,230
like you own this world?

936
00:41:56,760 --> 00:41:57,510
Do you

937
00:41:57,510 --> 00:41:58,960
drive this bus to work?

938
00:41:59,030 --> 00:41:59,800
Of course.

939
00:42:01,710 --> 00:42:03,480
What does your driver drive?

940
00:42:04,000 --> 00:42:05,280
A Mercedes.

941
00:42:06,000 --> 00:42:06,840
Actually,

942
00:42:06,960 --> 00:42:08,480
he's my dad's driver.

943
00:42:09,230 --> 00:42:10,000
I just

944
00:42:10,230 --> 00:42:11,280
can't stand being driven.

945
00:42:11,760 --> 00:42:13,230
So I always drive myself.

946
00:42:13,840 --> 00:42:15,280
From New Year's Eve to Lantern Festival,

947
00:42:15,280 --> 00:42:16,480
I drive this bus every day

948
00:42:16,920 --> 00:42:18,550
from Shenzhen to Guangzhou

949
00:42:18,710 --> 00:42:20,480
and back to Shenzhen.

950
00:42:21,760 --> 00:42:23,480
I even sleep in it.

951
00:42:28,920 --> 00:42:29,670
Ms. Fang,

952
00:42:30,280 --> 00:42:31,190
you seem surprised?

953
00:42:31,800 --> 00:42:33,400
Didn't my driver tell you

954
00:42:33,920 --> 00:42:35,800
I'm in the transportation business?

955
00:42:36,230 --> 00:42:37,070
Let me tell you.

956
00:42:37,550 --> 00:42:38,760
I have dozens of buses

957
00:42:38,960 --> 00:42:40,110
just like this.

958
00:42:40,360 --> 00:42:41,800
On the route between Shenzhen

959
00:42:41,800 --> 00:42:42,630
and Guangzhou,

960
00:42:42,760 --> 00:42:44,400
I have the most buses.

961
00:42:45,190 --> 00:42:46,960
I have no choice.

962
00:42:47,360 --> 00:42:49,760
All drivers went home for the holiday.

963
00:42:50,190 --> 00:42:50,920
And this is

964
00:42:50,920 --> 00:42:52,840
when we make the most money

965
00:42:52,840 --> 00:42:54,030
and have the most passengers.

966
00:42:54,320 --> 00:42:55,670
I can't afford to miss it.
